This directory should contain the following items:

- ewascatalog-studies.txt file
  contains metadata table from EWAS catalog
  obtained from:  https://www.ewascatalog.org/download/
  located under:  Download all meta-data
  exact address:  https://www.ewascatalog.org/static//docs/ewascatalog-studies.txt.gz

- ewascatalog-results.txt file
  contains results table from EWAS catalog
  obtained from:  https://www.ewascatalog.org/download/
  located under:  Download all results
  exact address:  https://www.ewascatalog.org/static//docs/ewascatalog-results.txt.gz

- KEPI_A_2289786_SM2258.xls file
  contains Crohn EWAS hits after adjustment for 12 immune cell types
  obtained from:  https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/15592294.2023.2289786
  located under:  Supplemental material > Supplementary Table 1.xls
  exact address:  https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/suppl/10.1080/15592294.2023.2289786/suppl_file/KEPI_A_2289786_SM2258.xls

- 42003_2026_9520_MOESM4_ESM.xlsx file
  contains interleukin-6 EWAS hits after adjustment for 12 immune cell types
  obtained from:  https://www.nature.com/articles/s42003-026-09520-2
  located under:  Supplementary information > Supplementary Data 1 to 20 (download XLSX)
  exact address:  https://static-content.springer.com/esm/art%3A10.1038%2Fs42003-026-09520-2/MediaObjects/42003_2026_9520_MOESM4_ESM.xlsx
